  Arena
  Elite
  Boss
  Map (map of bigger size than arena with fixed spawns)
  Unit shop
  Item shop
  Text + reward
  Training grounds (upgrade unit)
  Tavern (heal units)

Units die permanently when they die (dead units can be stored in bench to be revived later)
